title: HUNSTVILLE FIRST BAPTIST CHURCH VACATION BIBLE SCHOOL
content: Huntsville First Baptist Church will hold Vacation Bible School the week of June 4th thru the 8th from 12:30 to 3:30 pm. Kickoff will be held on Sunday, June 3rd at 6 pm. Come register your child for VBS on June 3rd and enjoy games, food and fun. For those children attending Summer School at Westran Elementary, they can walk with VBS adults from the school to the church, but a note must be sent to the school.
